🌟 DESCRIPTION🌟

Modern Warfare 2 has the most realistic missions In the series, I gathered together all the missions I think are the closest to actual combat scenarios.

Some missions start off realistic before diving Into the deep end, I decided to cut those parts while keeping what I thought was closest to real life.

I have military experience but not on the level of Special Forces, If you feel a mission should have been In the video Leave a comment about what mission and why so It may be added to the sequel video!
